<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>He is coming</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 The sun is rising for a new day
 And I will make my way today again
 This day may be special and surprising
 For you will stay on my side the whole day long
 It may happen at any moment, when it happens
 You will stay on my side the whole day long

[V2]
 You are coming very soon
 I'll be ready when it happens
 You are coming very soon
 I'll be ready when it happens
 It is surprising, believers are raising
 And flying high like feathers

[V3]
 Are you ready and prepared?
 All together we'll be flying
 Are you ready and prepared?
 All together we'll be flying
 Every believer meets Christ our Saviour
 High up in the air

[V4]
 This old body we will leave
 Let's enjoy it there's something better
 This old body we will leave
 Let's enjoy it there's something better
 What you are leaving
 just doesn't compare to the presence of His Glory

[V5]
 What a day it will be
 When His children enter into heaven
 What a day it will be
 When His children enter into heaven
 What you are leaving
 Just doesn't compare to the presence of His Glory

[V6]
 And every tear you have in your eyes
 The Lord Himself will wipe away
 There won't be anymore pain or dying
 Not even tears in our eyes or crying

[V7]
 Are you ready and prepared?
 He is coming very soon

[V8]
 Maybe tomorrow or even this hour
 He is moving in powerful ways
 calling out His People

[V9]
 For the Lord Himself will come down
 You will see all the angels in Heaven
 Shout out with their mighty voices
 The earth shakes with the trumpet sound

[V10]
 Are you ready and prepared?
 He is coming very soon...

[V11]
 Maybe tomorrow or even this hour
 He is moving in power
 Calling out his people
 Listen: &quot;I am coming very soon&quot;</lyrics>
<author>Livingospel</author>
<hymn_number>1928</hymn_number>
</song>